{"tid":101404,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有啲的士佬真係好過份","createTime":"2017-01-30T19:24:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-30T20:43:02.000Z","uid":39166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f5808168245bb530e3de597ec22eb8e9a4da9751","tid":101404,"uid":39166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T19:24:30.000Z","msg":"岩岩係KT睇完戲就打算上的士翻藍田<br />\n一上左車就講去邊啦<br />\n個司機一直都冇出聲<br />\n直到到左，個錶顯示23個幾到<br />\n俾左100，佢找緊錢期間個錶先跳左25.2<br />\n好記得係25.2<br />\n之後佢竟然收我26<br />\n我下左聲，我地就洛車<br />\n個的士佬竟然仲眼超超勁大聲話點啊"},{"pid":"5809f9bc5de72fc0894221b10801a9f2b32dbcb8","tid":101404,"uid":11171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T19:29:13.000Z","msg":"你唔好彩啦，的士佬好極端架，果幾蚊搭零凌晨車就算啦。"},{"pid":"13d3b90ae603bd13b92150cbc2cada452a4a125d","tid":101404,"uid":39166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T19:34:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你唔好彩啦，的士佬好極端架，果幾蚊搭零凌晨車就算啦。</blockquote>我明啊！其實有個重點，係佢找緊錢時，我特登想望一望個的士司機個塊名牌，但我發現佢係冇嘰。"},{"pid":"14d9a026c0640bfa0a94000dfd12b24fd19136fb","tid":101404,"uid":45232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T19:44:48.000Z","msg":"咁你都忍<br />\n唔恰你恰邊個"},{"pid":"47c1efcfa2396e039151affcf152e3299dd47f51","tid":101404,"uid":74497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T19:52:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁你都忍<br />\n唔恰你恰邊個</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cc4a6458b2f5ac26bc2f5a11c1ec4b85f0218b1","tid":101404,"uid":47879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T19:54:02.000Z","msg":"一係你豪俾佢當貼士，一係你即場開佢波<br />\n上嚟開post唔恰你恰邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee7ad82a8eda741276a900bb9d4e1a68fedf84f9","tid":101404,"uid":14036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T20:43:02.000Z","msg":"同埋兜路既正仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}